<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
		<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no,address=no">
		<title>注文確認｜コスモスターズ</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bulma.min.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/font-awesome.min.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery.slim.min.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<header class="header">
				<a href="http://www.cosmostars.co.jp/index.html" class="header-link"></a>
			</header>
			<section class="main">
				<div class="main-title has-text-centered">
					<h1>田中太郎様のお葬儀</h1>
					<p>
						<span class="main-title-sub-text">葬儀時間:<span>17:00</span>開始　</span>
						<span class="main-title-sub-text">ホール名:<span>ハクゼンホール安茂里会館</span></span>
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="progressbar">
					<div class="columns is-flex">
						<div class="column is-3-desktop is-3-mobile  progress-current ud-center">ご注文情報の入力</div>
						<div class="column is-3-desktop is-3-mobile  progress-outside ud-center">決済情報の入力</div>
						<div class="column is-3-desktop is-3-mobile  progress-outside ud-center">入力確認画面</div>
						<div class="column is-3-desktop is-3-mobile  progress-outside ud-center">完了</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<div class="order-confirm">
						<h2 class="sub-title">商品情報の確認</h2>
						<table class="table is-bordered">
					 		<tr>
					 			<td class="order-confirm-td-width order-confirm-td-bg">商品画像</td>
					 			<td class="order-confirm-td-bg">商品名</td>
					 		</tr>
					 		<tr>
					 			<td rowspan="3"><img alt="商品画像" src="img/haruka3.jpg" class="order-confirm-image-td-img"></td>
					 			<td class="order-confirm-td-detail">弔</td>
					 		</tr>
					 		<tr class="order-confirm-trh-adj">
					 			<td class="order-confirm-td-bg">価格</td>
					 		</tr>
					 		<tr>
					 			<td class="order-confirm-td-detail">1,500円</td>
					 		</tr>
					 		<tr>
					 			<td colspan="2" class="order-confirm-caution">
					 				<p class="has-text-left">上記価格は、台紙代＋お届け料となります。</p>
					 				<p class="has-text-left">サービスの性質上、キャンセルは葬儀の2時間前までとさせて頂きます。</p>
					 			</td>
					 		</tr>
						</table>
						<div class="button-adjust">
							<form action="item.html" method="get">
								<input type="submit" name="return" class="button button2" value="商品選択画面に戻る">
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="input-confirm">
						<div class="columns ud-center">
							<div class="column is-4 is-full-mobile payment-name">
								<span>総額(税込):</span>
							</div>
							<div class="column is-8 is-full-mobile payment-input">
								<span>1,500</span>円
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- ページトップへ戻るボタン -->
				<a href="#" id="page-top" class="page-top ud-center"><img src="img/page_top_logo.png" alt="ページトップへ戻る"></a>
			</section>
			<footer class="footer">
				<p class="footer-company">株式会社 コスモスターズ</p>
				<p class="footer-address">〒170-0013  東京都豊島区東池袋2-39-2</p>
				<p class="footer-tel">TEL03-3982-6226</p>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>